(120, 'Law Offices of Marc Blumenthal', 'service', NULL, 'lawyer, law office', NULL, '355 W Dundee Road Suite 200', 'Buffalo Grove', 'Illinois', '60089', '-87.966853', '42.137943', '(847)808-7090', NULL, 'www.marcjblumenthal.com', NULL, '', '', 'active', 'blumenthal_logo.jpg', NULL, '<strong>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">Chicago, Illinois native <strong>MARC J. BLUMENTHAL</strong> has always known he wanted to be a lawyer. Inspired by diverse individuals in the field of law as a youth, Mr. Blumenthal realized he wanted to participate in a profession where he, like the lawyers he admired, would have opportunities to affect positive changes in people&rsquo;s lives.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">After studying at the University of Illinois at Champaign, where he received a B.A. in History, Mr. Blumenthal attended the Illinois Institute of Technology Chicago-Kent College of Law, graduating in 1976. Upon graduation, Mr. Blumenthal chose to stay and practice law in Illinois, because he enjoys the strong sense of community in the Chicago area. Now, he brings more than thirty years&rsquo; experience in law to his role as the principal of the Law Offices of Marc J. Blumenthal, Ltd., located in Buffalo Grove, Illinois.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">Licensed in both federal and state courts, Mr. Blumenthal represents individuals and closely held corporations. Mr. Blumenthal provides personalized service, knowing that every client and set of facts is unique. Within the constraints of the law, Mr. Blumenthal works tirelessly to bring clients the best available solution to their problem.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">Mr. Blumenthal&rsquo;s practice concentrates on four complementary areas:</span></div>\r\n<div style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 15pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&middot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.marcjblumenthal.com/practice-areas/real-estate">real estate</a> </span></div>\r\n<div style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 15pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&middot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.marcjblumenthal.com/practice-areas/estate-planning">estate planning</a></span></div>\r\n<div style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 15pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&middot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.marcjblumenthal.com/practice-areas/business-transactions">business matters</a>, and</span></div>\r\n<div style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 15pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&middot;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.marcjblumenthal.com/practice-areas/transportation-law">transportation law</a>.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">Real estate clients often request that Mr. Blumenthal memorialize their legacy and protect their assets with an <a target="_blank" href="http://www.marcjblumenthal.com/practice-areas/estate-planning">estate plan</a>. Similarly, because Mr. Blumenthal understands the transportation industry, both from a legal and business perspective, he is able to provide greater assistance with corporate and legal challenges faced by players in the transportation industry. Whatever your legal matter, Mr. Blumenthal&rsquo;s unique subject-matter experience provides him with know-how rarely found in any one attorney.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">Mr. Blumenthal is active in the legal and business communities. As a director, as well as member, of the <strong>Illinois Real Estate Lawyers Association</strong>, he speaks at a variety of real estate seminars, both to professionals in the real estate field and members of the public. Additionally, Mr. Blumenthal&rsquo;s other affiliations, which reflect the diversity of his practice, include membership in the <strong>Illinois State Bar Association</strong> and the <strong>Transportation Lawyers Association</strong>. In concert with serving as a member of the <strong>Probate and Estate Planning Committee</strong> of the <strong>Northwest Suburban Bar Association</strong>, Mr. Blumenthal frequently contributes to that organization by presenting at its estate planning and probate seminars.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="FONT-SIZE: 8.5pt">In recent years, Mr. Blumenthal has become increasingly involved with local charities and non-profit organizations, using his legal experience to further his professional goal of making a difference in other people&rsquo;s lives. One rewarding pursuit has been working with <strong>Avenues to Independence</strong>, which assists developmentally disabled adults. Mr. Blumenthal, a long-time resident of Buffalo Grove, Illinois, currently serves as the President of the <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.buffalogrovechamber.org/about_us.asp">Buffalo Grove Chamber of Commerce</a></strong>.</span></div>\r\n</strong>', 'Monthly', 'Promotions', NULL, NULL),
(122, 'David`s Bistro', 'dining', 'Serving Lunch and Dinner', 'food, bistro, restaurant, French, catering', NULL, '883 Main St', 'Antioch', 'Illinois', '60002', '-88.096266', '42.478643', '(847)603-1196', NULL, 'http://www.davidsbistro.com', NULL, '', '', 'active', 'davidsbistro_logo.jpg', 'dbsandwich.jpg', '<div align="center">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://mm.suddenvalues.com/551/8355/image/header_copy.png" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style="BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(15,176,250) double; PADDING-RIGHT: 5px; BORDER-TOP: rgb(15,176,250) double; PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(15,176,250) double; BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(15,176,250) double; TEXT-ALIGN: center">\r\n	<font face="Times New Roman" size="6"><em><strong>David`s Bistro</strong></em></font></div>\r\n<div style="BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(15,176,250) double; PADDING-RIGHT: 5px; BORDER-TOP: rgb(15,176,250) double; PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 10px; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(15,176,250) double; BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(15,176,250) double; TEXT-ALIGN: center">\r\n	<p style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 20px">\r\n		883 MAIN STREET<br />\r\n		ANTIOCH, IL 60002<br />\r\n		Phone: 847.603.1196<br />\r\n		Fax: 847.603.1250<br />\r\n		<font face="Arial"><a href="mailto:dave@davidsbistro.com">dave@davidsbistro.com</a></font></p>\r\n	<p style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 20px">\r\n		<a href="http://ncw.suddenvalues.com/controller.cfm?handler=log&amp;action=bwc&amp;OrgID=8355&amp;nextPage=http://www.davidsbistro.com" target="_blank">www.davidsbistro.com</a></p>\r\n	<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 16px; TEXT-ALIGN: center">\r\n		<span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: rgb(4,50,143)">David`s Bistro will be open for lunch &amp; dinner Tuesday - Sunday from 11:00 am until David Kicks you out...<br />\r\n		<span style="FONT-STYLE: italic">nicely of course.</span></span><br />\r\n		Private events and full service catering are available everyday of the week. The Bistro bar is full service and makes a mean marti