(123, 'Dorfler`s Meat Market', 'retail', 'Quality You Can Taste', 'meat market, steaks, seafood, poultry', NULL, '1182 N. McHenry Rd', 'Buffalo Grove', 'Illinois', '60089', '-87.984333', '42.173772', '(847)459-3060', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 'active', 'dorflers_logo.jpg', NULL, '<p align="center">\r\n	<font size="4">The Highest Quality Meats, Seafood &amp; Poultry<br />\r\n	Serving Chicagoland and Across the USA</font></p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<font size="4"><font color="#993300" size="5">Dorfler`s Philosophy</font></font><br />\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4">We are committed to serving the finest quality products available.</font>&nbsp; We will fresh cut and hand trim any item the old fashioned way - exactly the way you want.&nbsp; We are committed to your 100% complete satisfaction every time, both with our products and with our service. </font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="style55">\r\n	<font size="4">We wouldn&rsquo;t have it any other way!</font></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="style55">\r\n	<font size="3"><font color="#993300" size="5">Dorfler`s&nbsp;Team</font><br />\r\n	<span class="style59"><span class="style60"><span class="style62"><span class="style63"><span class="style64"><span class="style79"><font color="#0000ff">Experienced<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledgeable<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Friendly<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dedicated</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="style61">\r\n	Over 200 Years of Collective Experience!</p>\r\n<p class="style56">\r\n	We love what we do and it shows.&nbsp; Meet us online or better yet, come in and meet us in person.&nbsp; We are waiting to serve you!</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="style56">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://images.suddenvalues.com/sudden/businesses/Creatives/395/3761/ScreenHunter_05 Sep. 16 19.27.jpg" /></p>\