(141, 'Home Helpers', 'service', 'Making Life Easier', 'old, help, healthcare, elderly, vacation, sick, grandparents', 'Regardless of age or ability, you value your independence. Whether youâ€™re a family caregiver or could benefit from assistance yourself, Home Helpers can make your life easier by providing compassionate in home care supportive services, including companion care, senior care and respite care so you or your loved one can enjoy aging in place in the comfort of home. From a few hours a week to 24/7 care, weâ€™ll tailor a flexible care plan to fit your needs and budget. At Home Helpers, weâ€™re more than just caregivers â€“ weâ€™re family.', '', 'Chicagoland', 'Illinois', '60026', '', '', '(847)685-0593', '', '', '', '2012-02-18', '', 'active', 'homehelpers_logo.jpg', 'homehelpers_photo.jpg', '<p align="center">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="dnn_ctr10871_ModuleContent">\r\n	<div class="Normal" id="dnn_ctr10871_HtmlModule_HtmlModule_lblContent">\r\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">\r\n			<span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: `Tahoma`,`sans-serif`"><font size="4" style="BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000">Welcome to Home Helpers of Northeastern Illinois! </font></span></p>\r\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">\r\n			<font size="5"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: `Tahoma`,`sans-serif`">Our only goal is to provide excellent home care for you and/or your loved ones. We can be reached 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Other than our own family, our clients are our top priority. Please spend some time on our site and then give us a call or email to find out more or to set up an appointment.<br />\r\n			<span style="FONT-FAMILY: `Tahoma`,`sans-serif`"><strong>(847) 685-0593<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>E-mail:&nbsp;</strong></span></span></font><font size="5"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt;