-serif; font-size: medium; "><span style="font-style: italic; ">Wa-Pa-Ghetti&#39;s Pizza has been a family owned and operated pizzeria since 1979. We are best known for our traditional Italian Style thick crust pizza, but we also make a thin crust and a sicilian style stuffed pizza upon request.<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Our dough is made fresh daily and is hand rolled in the traditional way. Our special sauce is homemade and we use a double layer of the finest cheese to give our pizza its great taste.<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					Wa-Pa-Ghetti&#39;s Pizza has won the Entertainment Members Choice Award for tastiest pizza, the Lake County Market Journal Pizzamania Contest, and the March Of Dimes Best Pizza in Town Award.<br />\r\n					<br />\r\n					With our competitive prices, professional service and our delicious variety of menu selections, why go anywhere else!</span></span></p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Half Off', 'Your Meal', 'Half Off', 'Your Meal'),
(144, 'JoS. A. Bank Clothier', 'retail', 'The Expert in Men`s Apparel', 'clothes, clothing, apparel, men`s apparel, suits, men`s suits', 'Find classic tailored and casual  menâ€™s clothing with a fit you can rely on at JoS. A. Bank. Our menswear collections offer quality, value and a complete guarantee of your satisfaction. Shop our large selection of sophisticated menâ€™s apparel today.', '2691 Navy Blvd.', 'Glenview', 'Illinois', '60025', '-87.824837', '42.090246', '(800)999-7472', NULL, NULL, 'service@jos-a-bank.com', '', '', 'active', 'josabank_logo.jpg', 'josabank_photo.jpg', '<table bgcolor="#ffffff" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n					<div class="generalparagraph">\r\n						<strong>Jos. A. Bank is not just another menswear retailer. What makes us unique is also what has attracted customers to our stores for 104 years; a heritage of quality and workmanship, an extensive selection of beautifully made, classically styled tailored and casual clothing, and prices typically 20 to 30 percent below our competitors. Add to that an expert staff of sales professionals who prize service and customer satisfaction above all, and you get the idea.</strong></div>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n					<img alt="" border="0" height="140" name="" src="http://www.josbank.com/wps/wcm/myconnect/64ed14004f856dac88d9bbac30c6e090/BizDress-Guideline-f09covr.jpg?MOD=AJPERES" width="115" /></blockquote>\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img alt="" border="0" height="140" name="" src="http://www.josbank.com/wps/wcm/myconnect/64ed14004f856dac88dbbbac30c6e090/BizDress-Guideline-f09pg31f.jpg?MOD=AJPERES" width="115" /></p>\r\n					<p align="center">\r\n						<img alt="" border="0" height="140" name="" src="http://www.josbank.com/wps/wcm/myconnect/64ed14004f856dac88e1bbac30c6e090/BizDress-Guideline-f09.jpg?MOD=AJPERES" width="115" /></p>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n				<blockquote>\r\n					We couldn`t have built a successful business without loyal customers, so at Jos. A. Bank our products are unconditionally guaranteed. Whether you shop online, at our stores, or through our seasonal catalogs, you`ll find that at Jos. A. Bank, service isn`t just a concept, it`s an everyday occurrence.<br />\r\n					<div class="generalparagraph">\r\n						To keep prices low, Jos. A. Bank has eliminated the middleman by working directly with some of the world`s best factories and workrooms. That means we can pass significant savings along to customers. But that doesn`t mean we scrimp on quality. Our buyers scour the globe for the finest fabrics with the richest textures and colors. Our tailors keep a close eye on every detail, adhering to the highest standards of fabric, fit and construction.</div>\r\n				</blockquote>\r\n				<ul>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class="generalparagraph">Over 450 stores nationwide with a full selection of men`s tailored and casual clothing, footwear and accessories</span></li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class="generalparagraph">4 seasonal catalogs mailed internationally with toll-free ordering in the US 24 hours a day 7 days a week</span></li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class="generalparagraph">100% guarantee of satisfaction behind every item we sell</span></li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class="generalparagraph">A heritage of 104 years of quality, value and service</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n				</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Benefits', 'Program', 'None at ', 'this time'),
(145, 'Peacock Marketplace & Professional Car Wash', 'service', 'Excellence in Car Washing for over 80 Years!', 'car wash, market, gas station', 'You''ll see the shining difference! We offer fuel, state-of-the art car cleaning, a large full featured market place and a deli style cafe. Join our Customer Loyalty Program for a Free Car Wash.', '860 S. Milwaukee Ave', 'Vernon Hills', 'Illinois', '60061', '-87.934962', '42.210292', '(847)821-1640', NULL, NULL, 'peacockoil@aol.com', '', '', 'active', 'peacock_logo.jpg', 'peacock_photo.jpg', '<p align="justify">\r\n	<font size="4">Our whole approach to excellence in car care is centered around one objective: Making your car, truck, or van look sparkling clean - and at a Surprisingly Low Cost.&nbsp; Around here, you`ll find the customer always comes first!</font></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<font size="3"><strong><font color="#ff0000" size="4">Save Big $`s Per Gallon at our<br />\r\n	24 Hour Mobil Gas Station</font></strong><br />\r\n	With Car Wash Purchase</font></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<font size="4">Car Wash Hours:<br />\r\n	Mon-Sat 7am-9pm<br />\r\n	Sun-7am-8pm</font></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<font size="4">860 S. Milwaukee Ave<br />\r\n	Vernon Hills, IL</font><br />\r\n	<font size="3">2 blocks North of Rt. 22</font></p>\r\n', 'Free', 'Car Wash', 'Half Off', 'Car Wash'),
(147, 'Nickel City', 'dining', 'Play Games, Win Prizes, All With Just Nickels!', 'redemption games, games, video games, ski ball, kids, arcade', 'Nickel City is the greatest Arcade and Family Entertainment Center with the                   Hottest Video and Redemption games', '555 Waukegan Rd', 'Northbrook', 'Illinois', '60062', '-87.828376', '42.145412', '(847)559-8727', NULL, 'www.nickelcitygames.com', 'amar@nickelcitygames.com', '', '', 'active', 'nickelcity_logo.jpg', 'nickelcity_photo.jpg', '<p align="center">\r\n	<font color="#000080" face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><strong>Affordable Fun for the Whole Family!!!!</strong></font></p>\r\n<div style="padding-right: 30px; padding-left: 10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(248, 201, 105);">\r\n	<div align="center">\r\n		<a href="http://www.nickelcitygames.com/" target="_blank"><font size="4">www.nickelcitygames.com</font></a></div>\r\n	<p align="justify">\r\n		<font color="#000080">Nickel City is the greatest Arcade and Family Entertainment Center with the Hottest Video and Redemption games. A $2 entry fee provides kids of all ages and adults with a diverse selection of over 100 exciting Video and Redemption games that all operate with Nickels. Thats right, here at Nickel City Arcade and Family Entertainment Center, we operate with JUST NICKELS. 30 Video games are on Free Play, No Nickels required! These free games include classic video games such as Pacman and Tetris. Perfect for the entire family, as best of all they are FREE. Nickel City also features hundreds of Redemption Prizes, Snack Bar, and a large Party Room to celebrate your special occasions! We specialize in birthday parties for all age groups.</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '$5 worth', 'of Free Nickels', '25% OFF', 'Birthday Party'),
(148, 'Philly G`s', 'dining', 'Pasta, Steaks, and Seafood', 'Italian, restaurant, steak, seafood, pasta, pizza, banquet', 'Lincolnshire ITALIAN RESTAURANT - ITALIAN FOOD - Lincolnshire - Philly G''s ITALIAN RESTAURANT Lincolnshire - ITALIAN FOOD Lincolnshire - Easy lookup of any restaurant in your area by restaurant name, food type, cuisine style in your city.   Find out what restaurants deliver, and their hours of operation. Find menus, wine lists, desserts and coupons of any restaurant in your area.', '1252 E. Highway 45', 'Vernon Hills', 'Illinois', '60061', '-87.981294', '42.229764', '(847)634-1811', NULL, 'www.phillygs.com', NULL, '', '', 'active', 'phillygs_logo.jpg', 'phillygs_photo.jpg', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<font face="Tahoma" size="2"><font size="3">Phil Gilardi, Jr. along with his uncle, Dan Sullivan, are proud to be carrying on the Gilardi tradition with Philly G`s. The menu offers a wide selection of pastas, chicken, steaks and seafood. Notable dishes include <em>Spinach Cappellacci, Chicken ala Gilardi, Skirt Steak</em> and <em>Parmigiana Crusted Salmon</em>. Philly G`s features an extensive wine list along with personalized catering services and private dining rooms.</font> </font></p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<font face="Tahoma" size="2"><a href="http://www.phillygs.com" target="_blank"><font size="4">www.phillygs.com</font></a></font></p>\r\n', '$25.00', 'Gift Certificate', '$25.00', 'Gift Certificate'),
(149, 'Murphy`s Health Foods & Juice Bar', 'retail', 'Full Service Health Foods Store', 'health, juice, gluten free, vitamins, aromatherapy', 'We specialize in the largest selection of vitamins, herbs and homeopathic medicines in Lake County.'' /><meta name=''keywords'' content=''murphys, murphy''s, health foods, juice, smoothies, vegetarian supplements, homeopathy, aromatherapy, wheat grass, juicer, carlson, enzymatic therapy, natures plus, enzymedica, garden of life , hemp, natural, wellness, organic, barleans, herbs, tea', '400 North Milwaukee Avenue', 'Libertyville', 'Illinois', '60048', '-87.953784', '42.286950', '(847)362-4664', NULL, 'http://www.metroalive.com/illinois/libertyville/murphyshealthfoodsjuicebar/', 'lorimurphy42@hotmail.com', '', '', 'active', 'murphys_logo.jpg', 'murphys_photo.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Welcome to Murphy`s Health Foods and Juice Bar, serving Lake County &amp; surrounding areas since 1971.</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Offering the largest selection of vitamins, herbs and homeopathic medicines in Lake County for nearly 15 years, Murphy&rsquo;s Health Foods &amp; Juice Bar has everything you need for a healthy lifestyle.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Our up to date, well educated staff will listen to your health needs and help you find the products that are right for you. We also host an on-site, monthly Well-being Workshop that will educate you on current health trends and provide tips for healthy living. Plus, our full-service juice bar offers a delicious variety of organic juices that will give you a boost of energy that lasts all day!<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Products we offer include, but aren&rsquo;t limited to:<br />\r\n	&bull; Vitamins and herbs<br />\r\n	&bull; Homeopathic remedies<br />\r\n	&bull; Organic groceries<br />\r\n	&bull; Organic hair and skin care<br />\r\n	&bull; Refrigerated and frozen vegetarian foods<br />\r\n	&bull; Aromatherapy oils and accessories<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Daily vegetarian lunch specials are available for dine in or carry out. Living a vegetarian lifestyle is a key ingredient to healthy living, and we believe after you try one of our delicious vegetarian meals, you&rsquo;ll be hooked for life! We also offer gluten free foods and supplements, as well as private consultations. We&rsquo;ll make sure all your health needs are covered.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Private consultations and workshops by Lori Murphy are available on a fee basis and by appointment only.</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<font size="4"><strong>Store Hours:</strong></font></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<font size="3">Monday - Friday 9-6<br />\r\n	Saturday 9-5<br />\r\n	Closed Sundays</font><br />\r\n	(Juice Bar closes one hour earlier)</p>\r\n', 'Free Berry', 'Smoothie', 'Free', 'Smoothie'),
(150, 'Photo''s Hot Dogs', 'dining', NULL, 'Restaurant, Food, Dining, Hot Dogs', NULL, '301 N. Northwest Hwy', 'Palatine', 'Illinois', '60067', '-88.033336', '42.117214', '(847)705-1111', NULL, 'www.photoshotdogs.com', 'photoshotdogs@yahoo.com', '', '', 'active', 'photos_logo.jpg', 'photos_photo.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<font color="#0000ff"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="6"><strong><font size="5">Photo`s Hot Dogs</font></strong></font><br />\r\n	<font size="4">Officially Crowned Hot Dog King of Chicago</font></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#000000" size="4">Serving the Chicagoland area with great hotdogs, burgers, sandwiches, salads, all at great prices!&nbsp; We have two locations to serve you in Palatine and Mt. Prospect.</font></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border="5" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 226px; height: 82px;" summary="" width="226">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<font face="Verdana" size="3"><font color="#000080" size="4"><strong>Photo`s HotDogs<br />\r\n					23 Years </strong><br />\r\n					<em>1989-2012</em></font></font></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<font size="3">We are proud to have served you for over 20 yrs!!&nbsp; Starting off with our first location in Mt. Prospect and our second location in Palatine, we couldn`t have done it without you!</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font color="#993300" size="4"><strong>Time are Tough; but Photo`s is TOUGHER!</strong></font><br />\r\n	We want to help stretch your dollar further and give you a happy, healthy<br />\r\n	and mouth-watering meals!&nbsp; We have lowered some of our most popular items to help you save in tough times.&nbsp; </font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4"><strong>Kid`s Meal ~ Only $3.99</strong></font><br />\r\n	<em>Nuggets, Grilled Cheese, Hot Dog<br />\r\n	Served with fries or apple slices and&nbsp;soft drink or milk</em></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4"><strong>High School&nbsp;Dollar Menu</strong><br />\r\n	<font size="3"><em>Choose any item from our dollar menu during your school lunch break</em></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4"><font size="3"><font size="4"><strong>HALF PRICE Coupons</strong></font><br />\r\n	<em>We are regularly adding new and different coupons on some of your most popular items.&nbsp; It`s easy to save, just click, print and use!</em></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4"><font size="3"><strong><font size="4">Daily Specials</font></strong><br />\r\n	<em>We have daily lunch specials starting at just $2.99!&nbsp; They change daily to give you variety and something new at Photo`s!</em></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font size="3"><font size="4"><font size="3"><strong><font size="4">HALF PRICE Happy Hour</font></strong><br />\r\n	<em>Everyday, from 3pm-5pm<br />\r\n	HALF PRICE on all Shakes</em></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left">\r\n	<font size="3"><font color="#000080" size="4">Photo`s Fund-Raising</font><br />\r\n	You`ve got to eat it; you might as well make some money doing it.<br />\r\n	Photo`s puts the fun back in Fun-Raising!<br />\r\n	<font face="Arial">We have thought of everything to ensure our customers the easiest experience when fundraising with us. You can leave all the hard work to us; we cook and we clean. Our motto has always been Use us, We love it! Whatever you need, we are here to help.<br />\r\n	<a href="http://photoshotdogs.com/fundraising/index.asp?mccategory=M" target="_blank">View our Fundraising webpage</a></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font face="Verdana" size="3" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Verdana" size="3" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="normal" rmuc5="0" wmby0="0">&nbsp;</span></font></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Monthly', 'Promotions', NULL, NULL);
