(164, 'The People''s Choice', 'dining', 'Over 43,000 Square Feet of Fun!', NULL, NULL, '2411 Grand Avenue', 'Waukegan', 'Illinois', '60085', '-87.863548', '42.369745', '847.360.8000', NULL, 'http://www.funwithrocky.com/', NULL, '', '', 'active', 'peopleschoice-logo.jpg', 'peopleschoice_photo.jpg', 'The Peopleâ€™s Choice Family Fun Center is the perfect venue for any type of family, corporate or group event. Located in the heart of Waukegan on Grand Avenue, Rte. 132, just 3 miles east miles of Six Flags Great America, The Peopleâ€™s Choice Family Fun Center has more than 43,000 square feet of FUN!!!\r\n\r\nAs you pass through the double glass doors you enter into this vibrant yellow arcade room featuring a carnival musical background offering more than 150 of the hottest redemption and arcade games for all ages. All games take tokens and upon completion, you are awarded tickets that you can redeem at our Redemption Counter which hosts over 1,000 prizes. Complete with an eye-popping redemption counter, the largest in the country offering an array of prizes for youth and adults; from hats to candy, toys, radios, books, stuffed animals, and so much more.\r\n\r\nPractice your golfing skills at Rockyâ€™s Fun House Miniature Golf, an 18 Hole, 4 Themed, Indoor, Glow-In-The-Dark Miniature Golf with a carnival and midway theme. Itâ€™s the most exciting, challenging and fun-filled holes of miniature golf in the Midwest. To learn more about our facility, please click on the tabs and tour our website.\r\n', 'Free', 'Birthday Spin', 'Free', 'Birthday Spin'),
